- Extensive experience with Elementor and other page builders.
- Strong understanding of technical SEO and experience with Google Search Console.
- Familiarity with web hosting environments and version control systems (e.g., Github, AWS and others).
- Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.
- Ability to work independently and as part of a team.
- Strong communication skills in both English and Hindi.
- Ability to coordinate and collaborate with various departments.

